# Workflow

1. Create a PR off a branch in `update-istio-APPVERSION` format
2. Check the MR, adapt when necessary, then merge
3. Release artifacts will be available at Release page
4. index.yaml is updated in Github Pages

# Settings

These are the settings required for the Actions scripts

- Secrets:
  - GH_TOKEN: This is Github token
- Variables
  - HELM_URL: This is the URL prefix of the gh-pages, eg. https://github.com/tetratelabs/charts/releases/download
